author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full three-song session of Corrine Bailey Rae, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Been to the Moon
00:03:24 The Skies Will Break
00:08:29 Like A Star

Musicians
Corrine Bailey Rae – vocals, guitar
Mikey Wilson – drums
John McCallum – guitar
Matt Walker – piano, bass
Steve Brown – piano

Credits
Video & Photo – Nate Ryan
Audio – Corey Schreppel
Production – Derrick Stevens
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
